ygData.messageBody:
Hello, everyone!

I am a 42 year old woman in Oregon. I'm fairly new to this list, but
have been playing EQ for over 3 years. My primary characters are on
Erollisi Marr, and I have many lowbies on other servers. The idea of
starting characters together on a single server sounds like alot of
fun. Count me in, if you go ahead with this. =)

Jean

--- In EQ_women@yahoogroups.com, "Torran" <torran@c...> wrote:
> EW.. that sounds good! Let me know when and where, and I'll join
you.
> Most of my chars are on Inny.
> *grin* Give a shout and I'll make plans to be there.=)
> <<>>Torran
>
